 spiritual dimension of Thoreau’s life to which his writings everywhere bear witness.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aReligion and literaturexHistoryx19th centuryxUnited States. 0aReligion and literaturezUnited StatesxHistoryy19th century. 0aReligion et littératurexHistoirex19e sièclexÉtats-Unis. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / American / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013z978311053799440uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030012975540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300129755423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300129755/original  a978-3-11-053799-4  Yale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles